    "Such dynamics accentuate project-based learning's efficacy in nurturing team collaboration, creativity, critical reasoning, and algorithmic understanding during middle school years.At the high school echelon, project-based learning's potency in amplifying critical reasoning stands out significantly, with an SMD value of 0.82 indicating a high impact.",
